'''Pugal''' is a big town in the [[Bikaner district]] of [[Rajasthan]], [[India]]. It is also the headquarters of the tehsil in the pugal Sub-division with the same name.<ref>[http://bikaner.nic.in/admn_setup.htm Bikaner Administrative Setup] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409231708/http://bikaner.nic.in/admn_setup.htm |date=2009-04-09 }}</ref>
==Geography== Pugal is located at {{Coord |28|30|00|N|72|48|0|E|display=inline}}. It has an average elevation of 145&nbsp;metres (869&nbsp;[[foot (length)|feet]]).<ref>[http://www.fallingrain.com/world/IN/24/Pugal.html Pugal Location]</ref>
==Demographics== {{As of|2001}} India [[census]], Pugal had a population of 6,314. Males constitute 3,416 of the population and females 2,898. <ref>[http://ourvillageindia.org/Place.aspx?PID=440427 Pugal Population]</ref>
